Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,織音妳看 是高南 是高南喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.24,Default-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fnＤＦクラフト遊W7\c&H0D8C00&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(960,985)}たかみな
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.24,註解J,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}たかみな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.24,註解C,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}高橋南
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看旁邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就播放了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在為了招募新同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第{\fe1\fnZhunYuan\fs70}77{\r}期研究生選拔開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是「去見粉絲的偶像」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是禁止藝能的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也會為各位獻上我們的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們承襲初代{\fe1\fnZhunYuan\fs70}AKB{\r}成員的名諱 並以此表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:10:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定妳也能承襲妳所憧憬的那個人喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是優子！ 那個時候的{\fe1\fnZhunYuan\fs70}Live{\r}有見到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的成長很多了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輪不到妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此 等候妳們的加入！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能遇見妳的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:18.24,金字,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be30}禁止藝能的星球的各位可用影像進行審查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:21.03,金字,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be30}為了安全起見 請加密後再傳送
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳這樣問…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我決定要參加喔！
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.11,0:10:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFGMaruGothic-Md}凪{\r}沙？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個時候的優子說想要見我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就要去見她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友歌唱得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有點像麻友友的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.04,Default-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fnＤＦクラフト遊W7\c&H0D8C00&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1007,985)}まゆゆ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.04,註解J,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}まゆゆ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.04,註解C,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}渡邊麻友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去 接下來換{\fe128\fnDFGMaruGothic-Md}凪{\r}沙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我有點不習慣唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有點害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就算能考上也上不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是幹勁還是好好傳達到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？ 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 織音就只會安慰她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:12:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來換織音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是試音會真的合格了怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對要襲名麻里子樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的話… 就是小指吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:14.37,Default-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fnＤＦクラフト遊W7\c&H0D8C00&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1100,985)}さっし
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.17,0:12:12.67,註解J,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}さっし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:12.67,註解C,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}指原莉乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,個性完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我先走…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,練習嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大會馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在害羞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友歌的男朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說還沒開始交往喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「好想見你」是為了跟喜歡的人告白吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上男孩子是怎樣的感覺啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友歌他們已經親親了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是什麼害羞的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟織音的話也做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開個玩笑而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少女們的思念穿越星際到達了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您執行神聖的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光吃番茄的話 臉會變得紅通通喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡番茄嘛！
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.98,0:13:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFGMaruGothic-Md}凪{\r}沙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:13:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的房間貼了張藝能的海報吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擅自進我的房間？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個星球還沒完全認可藝能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快撕下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那是好不容易才拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想珍藏下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有 剛剛在房間裡唱歌了吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.78,0:14:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是藝能管理局的人的家人在唱歌的話是會被說閒話的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.09,0:14:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFGMaruGothic-Md}凪{\r}沙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸這個大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也能成為偶像嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFGMaruGothic-Md}凪{\r}沙 我進去了喔？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:15:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛的髮圈 我也好想戴戴看
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.00,0:15:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFGMaruGothic-Md}凪{\r}沙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃這個吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸剛升上管理局的科長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滿腦子都想著規定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我歌唱得不好也是爸爸的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在家裡唱歌就會被罵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有門限所以不能在外面練習
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.32,0:15:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFGMaruGothic-Md}凪{\r}沙 妳也要體諒爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那誰來體諒我呢？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.27,0:15:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFGMaruGothic-Md}凪{\r}沙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽是站在爸爸那邊的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃完把盤子拿下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽做的飯糰什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 糟糕了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 友歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試 試 試 試 試…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試音會通過了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰通過了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看 還有到會場的電子車票
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三個人一起通過就像在作夢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？ {\fe128\fnDFGMaruGothic-Md}凪{\r}沙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFGMaruGothic-Md}凪{\r}沙？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始說要去的是妳啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說因為{\fe1\fnZhunYuan\fs70}AKB0048{\r}在等我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能通過我當然很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是爸爸絕對不會讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對自己唱的歌也沒自信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來以為考不上的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFGMaruGothic-Md}凪{\r}沙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還在怕什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遜咖！ 膽小鬼！ 遜咖！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遜咖 遜咖 遜咖！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 友歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一直都是我所嚮往的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在試音會時反藝能的激進派{\fe1\fnZhunYuan\fs70}DES{\r}隨時都會襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特地去冒這種險也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒用？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe1\fnZhunYuan\fs70}0048{\r}來見我們了喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四年前 這星球還是完全禁止藝能的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既使如此也還是來見我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFGMaruGothic-Md}凪{\r}沙 妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一天… 就是因為有了那場{\fe1\fnZhunYuan\fs70}Live
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以這個星球才改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不做的話就不會有改變！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡需要改變？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFGMaruGothic-Md}凪{\r}沙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用管她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有夢想是哪裡不對了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也還沒被選上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但妳是想被選上才去的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡過妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:19:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過試音會並成為偶像的妳 我是無法喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會被選上給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我成為{\fe1\fnZhunYuan\fs70}0048{\r}之後也絕對不會給你簽名的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來我也想跟{\fe128\fnDFGMaruGothic-Md}凪{\r}沙和友歌一起上學的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的各位都對我很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我能夠忘記寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到櫻花綻放之時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就再次在此相會吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟友歌說得一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又遜又膽小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友歌… 都那麼受傷了
